OL,3,CJersey updates law to make it illegal
OL,4,Cto bring knives onto school premises
OL,6,FA law regarding the possession of
OL,7,Foffensive weapons has been updated in
OL,8,FJersey today (Friday 18 October).
OL,10,FUnder the previous law, it was not
OL,11,Fillegal to carry a bladed or sharply
OL,12,Fpointed article on school premises,
OL,13,Fand prosecutors needed to prove intent
OL,14,Fto harm in public settings.
OL,16,FThe updated legalisation makes it an
OL,17,Foffence to carry any offensive weapon
OL,18,Fwithout reasonable excuse in public or
OL,19,Fon school premises.
