OL,3,CJersey updates law to make it illegal
OL,4,Cto bring knives onto school premises
OL,6,FThe legislation brings Jersey in line
OL,7,Fwith the current UK law which
OL,8,Fintroduces statutory offences related
OL,9,Fto public order and updates the legal
OL,10,Fframework around the possession of
OL,11,Foffensive weapons.
OL,13,FTo engage with young people, the
OL,14,FStates of Jersey Police say it will be
OL,15,Fworking closely with the Jersey Youth
OL,16,FService and schools to raise awareness
OL,17,Fand address the misconceptions around
OL,18,Fcarrying weapons.
